There has also been work on combining text and tables [chen2020hybridqa, chen2020open, zhu2021tat], or text, tables and images [talmor2021multimodalqa, hannan2020manymodalqa] for answering full-fledged questions.
However, these approaches cannot easily be extended to a conversational setting with incomplete follow-up questions.